                     <interp inst="t18421128-258-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18421128-cd-229" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18421128-258-offence-1 t18421128-cd-229"></join>13th of Nov</rs>., 7 panes of glass, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18421128-name-1330" type="victimName">
